dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Bus stops as of Service Change on August 24, 2014.

Changes since Previous Service Change:

Routes using N. Main St through the Hernandez Tunnel have been rerouted during construction to Washington - Houston - Crockett - Quitman. These routes include the 1 Hospital, 5 Kashmere, 9 North Main, 52 Hirsch, and 78 Irvington. The original routing on the west end of the 58 Hammerly has been modified to its original loop, but in reverse direction. Miscellaneous bus stop moves add and deletes are also included.
dataIdInfo.idPurp: Locations for boarding or alighting the Houston METRO bus system. This data is used for map display, query and analysis in Geographic Information System (GIS) software. This data is also imported into, and used in Trapeze FX, a bus scheduling software. From there, the bus stop locations are used for on-board stop announcements, ridership counts by stop, METRO and Google Trip Planners, and the METRO Customer Information Center.

prcStep.stepDesc: Routes Discontinued - 35 Fairview, 39 Parker, 48 W Dallas, 60 Hardy, 286 W Little York/NWTC/Greenway P&R, 313 Allen Parkway Shuttle Routes Restructured - 18 Kirby (replace 313), 37 El Sol, 48 Navigation (Magnolia TC Trips), 58 Hammerly (48 W Dallas), 67 Dairy Ashford (Original North end Configuration), 70 Memorial (48 W Dallas), 97 Settegast (All trips to Dividend @ Currency), 132 Harwin (Shift service from Holman to Elgin in Midtown)

Major updates include route restructure for West or North ends of routes 36 46 58. Also route change for routes 29 and 80 due to the closing of Tierwester on TSU campus. Restructure of route 75 to become the Eldridge Crosstown. The 67 Dairy Ashford is extended to serve the Addicks Park & Ride. Routes 52 and 87 were restructured on their Southern ends.
